 数据
 –1.学生表

Student(s_id,s_name,s_birth,s_sex) –学生编号,学生姓名, 出生年月,学生性别

–2.课程表

Course(c_id,c_name,t_id) – –课程编号, 课程名称, 教师编号

–3.教师表

Teacher(t_id,t_name) –教师编号,教师姓名

–4.成绩表

Score(s_id,c_id,s_score) –学生编号,课程编号,分数

题1 01课程比02课程分数高的学生

select a.s_id, c.s_name,a.s_score,b.s_score
from(
select s_id,c_id,s_score
from score
where
c_id = '01'
) as a
inner join
from(
select s_id,c_id,s_score
from score
where
c_id = '01'
) as b
on a.s_id = b.s_id
inner join student as c
on c_s_id = a.s_id
where a.s_score > b.score

题2 平均分>60的学号 平均成绩
select s_id,avg(s_score) as avgs
from score
group by s_id
having avgs>60

题3 所有学生的学号 姓名 选课数 总成绩
select a.s_id,count(b.c_id),sum(b.s_score)
from student as a
left join score as b 
on a.s_id = b.s_id
group by a.s_id

题4 查询姓侯的老师的个数
select ct(t_id)
from teacher 
where t_name like "hou%"

